https://docs.python.org/2/install/#alternate-installation-the-home-scheme
$ python setup.py install --home=~/Projects/Blue-Peninsula/bp-content/local --record=.files

2015-07-09
==========

Install lxml
http://lxml.de/installation.html#requirements
https://pip.pypa.io/en/latest/reference/pip_install.html#per-requirement-overrides
https://docs.python.org/2/install/#alternate-installation-the-home-scheme
$ sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt-dev python-dev
$ sudo pip install lxml --install-option="--home=/home/ubuntu/bp-content/local"

